    <div class="about-college">
      <h3>About Paro College of Education</h3>
      <p>
        Paro College of Education (PCE), established in 1975, is one of the oldest and most prestigious teacher education institutes under the Royal University of Bhutan.
        It is committed to preparing competent and reflective educators equipped to serve the nation.
      </p>
      <p>
        Located in the scenic valley of Paro, the college provides a conducive environment for learning and research. It offers a range of undergraduate and postgraduate programmes focused on teacher education, guidance and counselling, and inclusive education.
      </p>
      <p>
        The campus is well-equipped with hostels, academic blocks, IT and AV centers, a central library, and sports facilities. PCE emphasizes holistic development through academics, spiritual growth, and professional training.
      </p>
    </div>
