    <h3>PCE Admission Instructions & Eligibility</h3>
    <p><strong>Before applying</strong>, ensure you meet the eligibility criteria and have understood the course requirements.</p>

    <h4>Eligibility Criteria</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>Class XII pass students with English and Dzongkha competency</li>
      <li>Applicants passionate about education and community development</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>Application Process</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>Applications are made through RUB Online Admissions Portal</li>
      <li>Shortlisted candidates may be called for interviews or entrance tests</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>Funding Options</h4>
